      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's just not a new chapter though. that's the thing. it's not a blank page, it's just... gone. i feel like i've been running on a reserve that was never actually mine to begin with. everything feels so heavy, like i'm just dragging this empty shell of a person through days that don't mean anything. is it even worth trying to find something new when the core of who i was is just dead?",
